Philip Neustrom Theory is a newly minted field of Neustromnomic dadastatictics, a field somewhat related to bistromathematics and pantheistic solipsism.  It attempts to correlate Neustrom derived data with Fuzzy Math wiki statistics and events.  It is quite possibly the worlds only hope for a utopian existence.

  Philip Neustrom Theory Number One Theory Number One  A treatise on the Neustrom Paradox, similar to Zenos old quandary, but involving fewer arrows and trees and more pretty graphs.
  Philip Neustrom Theory Number Two Theory Number Two  A dire forecast revealing precisely how the well being of the wiki community is linked to Neustromnomics.
